{"tid":2254000,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"「沙德爾」逼港1號風球生效　天文台午夜後改發3號波","createTime":"2020-10-22T13:46:14.000Z","updateTime":"2020-10-22T13:53:02.000Z","uid":25823,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"57bd51fafeeb86ac4b644d0d34e11cc859105f7e","tid":2254000,"uid":25823,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-22T13:46:14.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/PuzMAKD.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FPuzMAKD.jpg&h=86a7b0fc&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n強烈熱帶風暴「沙德爾」已增強為颱風，並逐漸靠近廣東沿岸地區，並轉向偏西方向移動。天文台於今日(22日)下午5時40分發出一號戒備信號，按照預測路徑，「沙德爾」會繼續移近華南沿岸，與其相關的強風會逐漸影響珠江口一帶。天文台會在午夜後改發3號強風信號。"},{"pid":"8508aaf37297a184c8cc2f082e0f8058f4c1d332","tid":2254000,"uid":234553,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-22T13:47:05.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bouncer.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bouncer.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"baeb752d8fba8c67ee4abeeab76928bfecb185b9","tid":2254000,"uid":23445,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-22T13:50:16.000Z","msg":"好大雨<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bouncy.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bouncy.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"12c4c7403b87de1b9f18e36e5aae3b4fc8dfe235","tid":2254000,"uid":162674,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-22T13:51:23.000Z","msg":"黑衫條女<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1f15d118ac7c1bb61836d50d2bda26b285b8ea2e","tid":2254000,"uid":143241,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"12c4c7403b87de1b9f18e36e5aae3b4fc8dfe235","tid":2254000,"uid":162674,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-22T13:51:23.000Z","msg":"黑衫條女<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-22T13:53:02.000Z","msg":"輪廓唔夠深,典型港女樣"}]}